L4dZEfQkzDx1inl6wVQw">Nguyễn Xung Xác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-c%E1%BB%ADu-ph%C3%A1n-quan-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C3%A2u/poem-sNXpXpsYMVeaEqTO76eMyg">Tặng Điền cửu phán quan Lương Khâu - 贈田九判官梁邱</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/T%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1n/poem-DInmKN46UNRhteCjGhrwrw">Tự thán - 自嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-T%C3%B4-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-ntePeM4NDdtMaNEF9Lu2SA">Vịnh Tô Hiến Thành - 詠蘇憲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
